# ---- X-Ray / S.T.A.L.K.E.R. engine (external upstream dependency) ----------
# The X-Ray Monolith / xray-16 engine is a large upstream dependency and is NOT
# vendored in this repository. Obtain it separately (see README > Build
# Requirements) and place it under Engine/. It is excluded here to keep the
# STALKER-MP framework repository focused and reasonably sized.
Engine/
*.spawn
*.xrf
*.ogf
*.omf
*.dds
*.thm
*.geom
*.dxvk-cache

# ---- Third-party build artifacts (keep vendored sources, drop their builds)-
third_party/**/build/
third_party/**/_build/

# ---- AI collaboration / handoff artifacts (not part of the public codebase) -
# Internal AI-assisted workflow notes, session logs, and handoff docs are kept
# local and are NOT published to the public repository.
AI_START_HERE.md
**/AI_START_HERE.md
AI_Bootstrap.md
AI_CONTEXT.md
Documentation/AI/

# ---- Non-project / marketing assets (not part of the public codebase) ------
